<D>__{now what is it?}
<A>__{sammy points o.s. miss martin looks and freezes. as she moves down the hall, the camera pans with her until it gets two men standing near the entrance door. now the camera moves in to a three shot and we recognize george clews and his brother, bob. bob, his wrist bandaged, takes off his hat at miss martin's approach, and george noticing, does likewise.}
<C>__{george clews}
<D>__{the name's clews, ma'am mr. garvey sent us out }
